              <title>Innovation and Entrepreneurship Strategy Board (IESB)</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5435</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5435</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>This  is the ultimate innovation to create Knowledge Transfer Networks  (KTNs) from a wide variety of industries and form a Strategic Board at local diaspora. Its a next gen platform for entrepreneurs, academia and industry professionals to collaborate and help each other to solve problems quickly.</p>
<p>Focus areas:</p>
<p>1. Technology in Open Innovation</p>
<p>2. Research and Development</p>
<p>3. Information and Communication Technology</p>
<p>4.Investment Hub for creative ides</p>
<p>5. Strategic Business Partners: bring organisations and individuals together to share knowledge and secure funding for innovation</p>
<p>6. Technolgy for Environmental sustainability and healthcare</p>
<p>7. Food and Nutrition</p>
<p>8. Empower&nbsp; students to reshape the education system</p>
<p>9. Social Enterprise and sustainable economy</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
